  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377900/extras/bac40bcc7273a8a33257f2353b347cf5.avif?t=1737878631\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377900/extras_big/bac40bcc7273a8a33257f2353b347cf5.avif?t=1737878631 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Adventure Exploration</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During your adventures in Dice Clash World, you'll be free to uncover every mystery on the map like a true explorer, searching for hidden treasures and facing unknown challenges. From the quiet moonlight forest to the bitterly cold cloud-topped ice city, every choice and every move may change your fate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377900/extras/c67bb2168c410a0bc775117049202cc4.avif?t=1737878631\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377900/extras_big/c67bb2168c410a0bc775117049202cc4.avif?t=1737878631 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dice Mechanism</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each hero has his own unique dice. Determine your actions and the outcome of battles by throwing customized dice, each throw is destiny, making your adventure full of uncertainty and surprises.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377900/extras/32d8dc2e4d1eb890d7e9b9484b8a6729.avif?t=1737878631\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377900/extras_big/32d8dc2e4d1eb890d7e9b9484b8a6729.avif?t=1737878631 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Card Strategy</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect all kinds of magic cards and build your own deck. Each card has its own unique magic and skills, and the key to victory is to play your cards wisely and strategically.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377900/extras/7b530e1b42cf630e27d1e9f78033ec9e.avif?t=1737878631\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377900/extras_big/7b530e1b42cf630e27d1e9f78033ec9e.avif?t=1737878631 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Roguelike Mechanics</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In each reincarnation, the world will take on a randomized appearance, the souls of the brave are never extinguished, and each rebirth is a continuation of hope.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377900/extras/3e670c9731c76a3f11f3f0e802b60c55.avif?t=1737878631\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377900/extras_big/3e670c9731c76a3f11f3f0e802b60c55.avif?t=1737878631 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377900/extras/bac40bcc7273a8a33257f2353b347cf5.avif?t=1737878631\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377900/extras_big/bac40bcc7273a8a33257f2353b347cf5.avif?t=1737878631 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Adventure Exploration</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During your adventures in Dice Clash World, you'll be free to uncover every mystery on the map like a true explorer, searching for hidden treasures and facing unknown challenges. From the quiet moonlight forest to the bitterly cold cloud-topped ice city, every choice and every move may change your fate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377900/extras/c67bb2168c410a0bc775117049202cc4.avif?t=1737878631\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377900/extras_big/c67bb2168c410a0bc775117049202cc4.avif?t=1737878631 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dice Mechanism</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each hero has his own unique dice. Determine your actions and the outcome of battles by throwing customized dice, each throw is destiny, making your adventure full of uncertainty and surprises.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377900/extras/32d8dc2e4d1eb890d7e9b9484b8a6729.avif?t=1737878631\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377900/extras_big/32d8dc2e4d1eb890d7e9b9484b8a6729.avif?t=1737878631 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Card Strategy</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect all kinds of magic cards and build your own deck. Each card has its own unique magic and skills, and the key to victory is to play your cards wisely and strategically.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377900/extras/7b530e1b42cf630e27d1e9f78033ec9e.avif?t=1737878631\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377900/extras_big/7b530e1b42cf630e27d1e9f78033ec9e.avif?t=1737878631 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Roguelike Mechanics</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In each reincarnation, the world will take on a randomized appearance, the souls of the brave are never extinguished, and each rebirth is a continuation of hope.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377900/extras/3e670c9731c76a3f11f3f0e802b60c55.avif?t=1737878631\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377900/extras_big/3e670c9731c76a3f11f3f0e802b60c55.avif?t=1737878631 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
